, 0.63, 1.06, and 1.27 um) by a next generation\ndirect-imaging telescope such as LUVOIR/HDST or HabEx and would indicate an\noxygen atmosphere too massive to be biologically produced.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Feb 2016 21:00:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-29"}
