emblies of thousands of fibers. We use our method\nto investigate two important questions in the mechanics of cell division: (i)\nthe effect of confinement on the hydrodynamic mobility of microtubule asters;\nand (ii) the dynamics of the positioning of mitotic spindle in complex cell\ngeometries.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Feb 2016 01:42:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-04"}
