 cognition and cooperation are supported in cellular\nnetworks, as compared to the conventional direct transmission, pure cognition\nand pure cooperation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Feb 2016 15:18:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-19"}
